<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Booking Invoice</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 40px;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333;
      }
      .invoice-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: auto;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007aff;
      }
      .title {
        text-align: right;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .title small {
        font-size: 14px;
        display: block;
        font-weight: normal;
        margin-top: 5px;
      }
      .section {
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .section p {
        font-size: 15px;
        margin: 6px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 5px solid #007aff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .highlight-box p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .note {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
      .btn {
        background-color: #007aff;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="invoice-container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="title">
          Booking Invoice
          <small>
            Invoice Date: <%= new Date(bookingDate).toLocaleDateString() %><br />
            Due: <%= new Date(bookingDate).toLocaleDateString() %>
          </small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <p><strong>Customer Name:</strong> <%= userName %></p>
        <p><strong>Tour Title:</strong> <%= tourTitle %></p>
        <p>
          <strong>Booking Date:</strong> <%= new
          Date(bookingDate).toLocaleDateString() %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Guest Count:</strong> <%= guestCount %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <p><strong>Payment ID:</strong> <%= transactionId %></p>
        <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> $<%= totalAmount.toFixed(2) %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        Prototype-based programming is a style of object-oriented programming in
        which behaviour...
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <a href="#" class="btn">Download Invoice PDF</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
